Author: my-destructive-side
Text: General Tso tofu, pad Thai, Thai fried rice with tofu, most vegetarian Indian dishes (especially biryani, samosas, and anything with paneer). I’m a sucker for spicy foods.  Also grilled cheese, pizza, mashed potatoes, and poached or fried eggs.

Author: killadamsandler
Text: Peanut butter in/on anything. Peanut butter by itself, too. When I’m restricting heavily I often have dreams about peanut butter lol.
